1. *Ispada* da nismo stigli na vreme. (It turns out we didn't arrive on time.)
2. On *ispada* iz društva već godinama. (He's been dropping out of society for years.)
3. *Ispada* da ne znaš šta radiš. (It seems like you don't know what you're doing.)
4. Nije fer da *ispadaš* iz takmičenja samo zato što nisi dovoljno jak. (It's not fair that you're dropping out of the competition just because you're not strong enough.)
5. Ona *ispada* veoma dobra u matematici. (She appears to be very good at math.)
6. Zašto mi *ispadaš* tako hladan? (Why are you coming across as so cold to me?)
7. Nikad neću zaboraviti kako si *ispao* hrabar u teškoj situaciji. (I'll never forget how brave you were in a difficult situation.)
8. *Ispada* da je to bilo samo moje maštanje. (It turns out it was just my imagination.)
9. On *ispada* iz uloge kad god treba da igra glavnu scenu. (He's dropping out of character every time he needs to play the main scene.)
10. Ti *ispadaš* kao da si u pravu, ali zapravo nisi. (You seem like you're right, but you're actually not.)